						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Hero-stone near the Śiddhēśvara temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>Rāmachandra—A.D. 1275.</p>						

						<p>This inscription is dated in the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Yuva</hi> during the reign of <hi rend="bold">Rāmadēvā, Chaitra ba. 11, Sunday,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1275, March 11, Sunday.</hi></p>						

						<p>It commemorates the death of <hi rend="bold">Jōyi-Nāyaka</hi> of <hi rend="bold">Hāvēri</hi> who marched against (Narasiha) of <hi rend="bold">Dōrasamudra</hi> and died in the presence of <hi rend="bold">[Jōya]-Daḷavaya.</hi> </p>						

						</summary>
